[Any Value Seems To Prevent Enemies From Grabbing You]
author=VisitntX
description=They can still hit you. It might be very buggy though, I found the same code for File 1 and it had side effects. In File 1 when certain enemies did some sort of grab attack the game stopped (ants jumping on you, the dog biting your arm). I don&#039;t know if that still happens in File 2, but I know it&#039;s safe with zombies.
patch=1,EE,204C6944,extended,00000000

