[Health Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Set it to all F&#039;s for full health, or 0 to crawl.
patch=1,EE,204C6350,extended,00000000

[How Fast You Do Certain Things Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=These are the things I confirmed:
Reload speed
Tackling speed (if you hit something with the tackle the speed is normal, but if you keep tackling and don&#039;t hit anything you will still tackle very fast)
D-Pad turning only speed
picking up items speed
refire speed
equipping/unequipping weapons speed
melee weapon attack speed

40800000 - fast
Don&#039;t make it too fast, or tackles and melee weapons can&#039;t hit anything.
patch=1,EE,204C69D0,extended,40800000

